548
00:32:46,910 --> 00:32:51,230
I don't understand what you are saying.

549
00:32:51,230 --> 00:32:52,639
You don't understand?

550
00:32:52,640 --> 00:32:55,129
You went to see Chu Chu in front of Jinli on purpose,

551
00:32:55,130 --> 00:32:57,349
