569
00:33:39,800 --> 00:33:41,499
Say it!  Why do you want to kill Miss Chu?

570
00:33:41,499 --> 00:33:43,919
Say it! Why do you have to kill Chu Chu?

571
00:33:43,920 --> 00:33:46,830
Commandery Prince An. General Xiao.

572
00:33:47,550 --> 00:33:50,059
Chu Chu is the daughter of the person who killed your father.

573
00:33:50,060 --> 00:33:51,839
What?

574
00:33:51,840 --> 00:33:54,869
Vice Minister Jing, do you still remember the hairpin we rubbed?

575
00:33:54,869 --> 00:33:56,669
